## User Story

As a **developer**, I want to **refactor the authentication code**, so that it becomes easier to maintain and less prone to errors.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 1**: Break down the authentication code into smaller, reusable functions.
- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 2**: Write unit tests for the authentication functions.

## Tasks

- [ ] **Task 1**: Refactor the login and registration logic into separate functions.
- [ ] **Task 2**: Write unit tests for authentication logic.

